重窃取国家机密罪的处罚；并把颠覆中央人民政府罪，修订为颠覆国家政权罪；增加试图推翻等罪，涵盖其他非暴力非法手段做出的颠覆行为。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ilr/U0oD32IxmEAMaCDg1Mzc1NTc4IN6rkJkGMAQ4pwFACXIJNTUzOTE1Njk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"190 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-3d9d53cab4dfa1755c5aeb8c2670a216_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1663390769.4970863","card_id":"Q_553981693","target":{"id":553981693,"title":"卢甘斯克总检察长在爆炸中丧生，俄乌局势最新进展如何？有哪些信息值得关注？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/553981693","type":"question","created":1663329556,"answer_count":112,"follower_count":246,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4621,5548,30738,95563,1941710],"comment_count":11,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"据今日俄罗斯报道，9月16日，卢甘斯克总检察长谢尔盖·戈尔宾科在卢甘斯克中心政府大楼爆炸中受伤身亡。目前，检察院的工作人员已被疏散，急救人员正在现场开展救援工作。"},"attached_info":"ClUIlr/U0oD32IxmEAMaCDg1MzkwMjk0IJTKkZkGMAs49gFACnIJNTUzOTgxNjkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"170 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fafb04e3765b80828901663a62278ba2_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1663390769.4980752","card_id":"Q_447345247","target":{"id":447345247,"title":"全款买车和贷款买车，差距有多大？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/447345247","type":"question","created":1614741791,"answer_count":101,"follower_count":437,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[123411,128471,131133,132225,132869],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Ilr/U0oD32IxmEAMaCDYxNjg4NjE4IJ+C/IEGMAE4tQNAC3IJNDQ3MzQ1MjQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"150 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer",